            },
            "date": "2016-06-08 13:48:34.000000000",
            "message": "Abandoned\n\nThanks everyone for reviews. I will add documentation for the need for lite-specs. And how they differentiate with api & other docs, also with release notes.\n\nFor Newton, planning to go with Erno's proposal for lite-specs.",
